reviewText: A must have for any anime enthusiast.

in this set many things happen that keep u on your feet great space battles with the gundams and anyone thats fans of machine anime action this series and dvd set is one to have if u don't have it 4 stars cause it does not fail you as a gundam series fan
over all really good but since i bought it used there were problems with the final episode on disc 2

Things I would like to see in the next TRANSFORMERS movie; OMEGA SUPREME as an Aircraft Carrier! Imagine with Michael Bay construction Devastator from the Second Movie, what will the outcome of the 2 largest Transformers duking it out in all combat melee fighting!
This is great!! i do hope Bandi gets it back  together and keep making Blu Rays and DVDs all we can do is wait
It was brand new when I receive the item. I needed this item for my collection. Luv the Gundam 00 series.
